    "body": "### Problem\n\nFor cjk fonts, the default character spacing is not suitable for reading. cjk fonts must be individually adjusted to achieve correct character spacing display.\r\n![image](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/assets/31800073/49a5f95b-1b42-47f9-9beb-fb9cf4ea278b)\r\n\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nJust like what wezterm does, you can adjust the zoom size of a certain font individually.\r\n\r\n![image](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/assets/31800073/49f692bb-75a3-4cdc-abc7-87f02a32aab5)\r\n\r\nThe effect is as shown\r\n\r\n![image](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/assets/31800073/dc82a47b-9aaf-459b-8f52-63c73fe452bc)\r\n\r\n",
